('ALIGNED_OIL', 'consumables', 'Aligned Oil', '9', NULL, '140', NULL, 'L', NULL, 'held in 2 hands', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'This oil fills a weapon with cosmic power of an alignment. Each <i>aligned oil</i> is crafted to one alignment: chaos, evil, good, or law (such as a <i>good-aligned oil</i>). A weapon anointed with this oil gains the effects of the property rune matching its alignment: 
