('ANTIMAGIC_OIL', 'consumables', 'Antimagic Oil', '20', NULL, '13000', NULL, 'L', NULL, 'held in 2 hands', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'This oil contains energy that repels nearly all types of magic. When you apply this oil to armor, the creature wearing the armor becomes immune to all spells, effects of magic items (the wearer’s and those of others), and effects with the magical trait for 1 minute. The oil affects neither the magic of the armor nor the fundamental runes of weapons attacking the wearer. Magical effects from a source of 20th level or higher, such as a deity, still function on the armor’s wearer.<br><br><b>Activate</b>  Interact', NULL, 'https://2e.aonprd.com/Equipment.aspx?ID=172'),
('OIL_OF_POTENCY', 'consumables', 'Oil of Potency', '2', NULL, '7', NULL, 'L', NULL, 'held in 2 hands', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'When you apply this thick, viscous oil to a non-magical weapon or suit of armor, that item immediately becomes magically potent. If the item is a weapon, it temporarily becomes a <i>+1 striking weapon</i>, or, if it’s armor, it temporarily becomes <i>+1 resilient armor</i>. This lasts for 1 minute.<br><br><b>Activate</b>  Interact', NULL, 'https://2e.aonprd.com/Equipment.aspx?ID=179'),
('HEALING_POTION_MODERATE', 'consumables', 'Healing Potion (Moderate)', '6', NULL, '50', NULL, 'L', NULL, 'held in 1 hand', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'A healing potion is a vial of a ruby-red liquid that imparts a tingling sensation as the drinker’s wounds heal rapidly. When you drink a healing potion, you regain the listed number of Hit Points.<br><br><b>Activate</b>  Interact<br><br><b>Healing Potion (Minor) Item 1</b><br><b>Level</b> 1; <b>Price</b> 4 gp<br>The potion restores 1d8 Hit Points.<br><br><b>Healing Potion (Lesser) Item 3</b><br><b>Level</b> 3; <b>Price</b> 12 gp<br>The potion restores 2d8+5 Hit Points.<br><br><b>Healing Potion (Moderate) Item 6</b><br><b>Level</b> 6; <b>Price</b> 50 gp<br>The potion restores 3d8+10 Hit Points.<br><br><b>Healing Potion (Greater) Item 12</b><br><b>Level</b> 12; <b>Price</b> 400 gp<br>The potion restores 6d8+20 Hit Points.<br><br><b>Healing Potion (Major) Item 18</b><br><b>Level</b> 18; <b>Price</b> 5,000 gp<br>The potion restores 8d8+30 Hit Points.', NULL, 'https://2e.aonprd.com/Equipment.aspx?ID=186'),
