('OIL_OF_REPULSION', 'consumables', 'Oil of Repulsion', '11', NULL, '175', NULL, 'L', NULL, 'held in 2 hands', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'This oil contains magnetically charged iron filings repelled into opposite ends of the vial. For 1 minute after you apply this oil to armor, any creature that hits you with a melee Strike must attempt a DC 28 Fortitude save with the following effects.<br><br><b>Activate</b>  Interact<br><br><b>Success</b> The creature is unaffected.<br><b>Failure</b> The creature is pushed up to 10 feet away from you (the GM determines the direction).<br><b>Critical Failure</b> As failure, and the creature is also knocked prone.', NULL, 'https://2e.aonprd.com/Equipment.aspx?ID=180'),
