('COMPASS', 'equipment', 'Compass', '0', NULL, '1', NULL, 'L', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'A compass helps you Sense Direction or navigate, provided you’re in&nbsp;a location with uniform magnetic fields. Without a compass, you take a –2 item penalty to these checks (similar to using a shoddy item). A lensatic compass gives you a&nbsp;+1 item bonus to&nbsp;these checks.', NULL, 'https://2e.aonprd.com/Equipment.aspx?ID=16'),
