('CROWBAR', 'equipment', 'Crowbar', '0', NULL, '0.5', NULL, 'L', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'When Forcing Open an object that doesn’t have an easy grip, a crowbar makes it easier to gain the necessary leverage. Without a crowbar, prying something open takes a –2 item penalty to the Athletics check to Force Open (similar to using a shoddy item). A levered crowbar grants you a +1 item bonus to Athletics checks to Force Open anything that can be pried open. ', NULL, 'https://2e.aonprd.com/Equipment.aspx?ID=18'),
