('DISGUISE_KIT', 'equipment', 'Disguise Kit', '0', NULL, '2', NULL, 'L', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'This small wooden box contains cosmetics, false facial hair, spirit gum, and a few simple wigs. You usually need a disguise kit to set up a disguise in order to Impersonate someone using the Deception skill. An elite disguise kit adds a +1 item bonus to relevant checks. If you’ve crafted a large number of disguises, you can replenish your cosmetics supply with replacement cosmetics suitable for the type of your disguise kit.', NULL, 'https://2e.aonprd.com/Equipment.aspx?ID=19'),
