('DARKVISION_ELIXIR_LESSER', 'alchemical', 'Darkvision Elixir (Lesser)', '2', NULL, '6', NULL, 'L', NULL, 'held in 1 hand', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'After you drink this elixir, your sight becomes sharper in darkness. You gain darkvision for the listed duration.<br><br><b>Activate</b>  Interact<br><br><b>Darkvision Elixir (Lesser) Item 2</b><br><b>Level</b> 2; <b>Price</b> 6 gp<br>The duration is 10 minutes.<br><br><b>Darkvision Elixir (Moderate) Item 4</b><br><b>Level</b> 4; <b>Price</b> 11 gp<br>The duration is 1 hour.<br><br><b>Darkvision Elixir (Greater) Item 8</b><br><b>Level</b> 8; <b>Price</b> 90 gp<br>The duration is 24 hours.', NULL, 'https://2e.aonprd.com/Equipment.aspx?ID=89'),
('SERENE_MUTAGEN_MODERATE', 'alchemical', 'Serene Mutagen (Moderate)', '3', NULL, '12', NULL, 'L', NULL, 'held in 1 hand', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'You gain inner serenity, focused on fine details and steeled against mental assaults, but you find violence off-putting.<br><br><b>Benefit</b> You gain an item bonus to Will saves and Perception, Medicine, Nature, Religion, and Survival checks. This bonus improves when you attempt Will saves against mental effects. <br><br><b>Drawback</b> You take a –1 penalty to attack rolls and save DCs of offensive spells, and a –1 penalty per damage die to all weapon, unarmed attack, and spell damage.<br><br><b>Activate</b>  Interact<br><br><b>Serene Mutagen (Lesser) Item 1</b><br><b>Level</b> 1; <b>Price</b> 4 gp<br>The bonus is +1, or +2 vs. mental, and the duration is 1 minute.<br><br><b>Serene Mutagen (Moderate) Item 3</b><br><b>Level</b> 3; <b>Price</b> 12 gp<br>The bonus is +2, or +3 vs. mental, and the duration is 10 minutes.<br><br><b>Serene Mutagen (Greater) Item 11</b><br><b>Level</b> 11; <b>Price</b> 300 gp<br>The bonus is +2, or +3 vs. mental, and the duration is 10 minutes.<br><br><b>Serene Mutagen (Major) Item 17</b><br><b>Level</b> 17; <b>Price</b> 3,000 gp<br>The bonus is +4, and the duration is 1 hour. When you roll a success on a Will save against a mental effect, you get a critical success instead, and your critical failures on Will saves against mental effects become failures instead.', NULL, 'https://2e.aonprd.com/Equipment.aspx?ID=100'),
('WINTER_WOLF_ELIXIR_LESSER', 'alchemical', 'Winter Wolf Elixir (Lesser)', '4', NULL, '15', NULL, 'L', NULL, 'held in 1 hand', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'This elixir warms your core and improves your circulation. For 24 hours, you are protected from the effects of severe cold.<br><br><b>Activate</b>  Interact<br><br><b>Winter Wolf Elixir (Lesser) Item 4</b><br><b>Level</b> 4; <b>Price</b> 15 gp<br><br><b>Winter Wolf Elixir (Moderate) Item 12</b><br><b>Level</b> 12; <b>Price</b> 320 gp<br>You’re also protected from extreme cold.<br><br><b>Winter Wolf Elixir (Greater) Item 16</b><br><b>Level</b> 16; <b>Price</b> 1,400 gp<br>You’re also protected from extreme and incredible cold.', NULL, 'https://2e.aonprd.com/Equipment.aspx?ID=103'),
('QUICKSILVER_MUTAGEN_MAJOR', 'alchemical', 'Quicksilver Mutagen (Major)', '17', NULL, '3000', NULL, 'L', NULL, 'held in 1 hand', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Your features become thin and angular. You become swifter and nimbler, but your body also becomes&nbsp;fragile. <br><br><b>Benefit</b> You gain an item bonus to Acrobatics checks, Stealth checks, Thievery checks, Reflex saves, and ranged attack rolls, and you gain the listed status bonus to your Speed.<b>Drawback</b> You take damage equal to twice your level; you can’t recover Hit Points lost in this way by any means while the mutagen lasts. You take a –2 penalty to Fortitude saves.<br><br><b>Activate</b>  Interact<br><br><b>Quicksilver Mutagen (Lesser) Item 1</b><br><b>Level</b> 1; <b>Price</b> 4 gp<br>The bonus to rolls is +1, the bonus to Speed is +5 feet, and the duration is 1 minute.<br><br><b>Quicksilver Mutagen (Moderate) Item 3</b><br><b>Level</b> 3; <b>Price</b> 12 gp<br>The bonus to rolls is +2, the bonus to Speed is +10 feet, and the duration is 10 minutes.<br><br><b>Quicksilver Mutagen (Greater) Item 11</b><br><b>Level</b> 11; <b>Price</b> 300 gp<br>The bonus to rolls is +3, the bonus to Speed is +15 feet, and the duration is 1 hour.<br><br><b>Quicksilver Mutagen (Major) Item 17</b><br><b>Level</b> 17; <b>Price</b> 3,000 gp<br>The bonus to rolls is +4, the bonus to Speed is +20 feet, and the duration is 1 hour.', NULL, 'https://2e.aonprd.com/Equipment.aspx?ID=97'),
('ELIXIR_OF_LIFE_LESSER', 'alchemical', 'Elixir of Life (Lesser)', '5', NULL, '30', NULL, 'L', NULL, 'held in 1 hand', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Elixirs of life accelerate the body’s natural healing processes and immune system. Upon drinking this elixir, you regain the listed number of Hit Points and gain an item bonus to saving throws against diseases and poisons for 10 minutes.<br><br><b>Activate</b>  Interact<br><br><b>Elixir of Life (Minor) Item 1</b><br><b>Level</b> 1; <b>Price</b> 3 gp<br>The elixir restores 1d6 Hit Points, and the bonus is +1.<br><br><b>Elixir of Life (Lesser) Item 5</b><br><b>Level</b> 5; <b>Price</b> 30 gp<br>The elixir restores 3d6+6 Hit Points and the bonus is +1.<br><br><b>Elixir of Life (Moderate) Item 9</b><br><b>Level</b> 9; <b>Price</b> 150 gp<br>The elixir restores 5d6+12 Hit Points, and the bonus is +2.<br><br><b>Elixir of Life (Greater) Item 13</b><br><b>Level</b> 13; <b>Price</b> 600 gp<br>The elixir restores 7d6+18 Hit Points, and the bonus is +2.<br><br><b>Elixir of Life (Major) Item 15</b><br><b>Level</b> 15; <b>Price</b> 1,300 gp<br>The elixir restores 8d6+21 Hit Points, and the bonus is +3.<br><br><b>Elixir of Life (True) Item 19</b><br><b>Level</b> 19; <b>Price</b> 3,000 gp<br>The elixir restores 10d6+27 Hit Points, and the bonus is +4.', NULL, 'https://2e.aonprd.com/Equipment.aspx?ID=91'),
('ENERGY_MUTAGEN_MAJOR', 'alchemical', 'Energy Mutagen (Major)', '17', NULL, '3000', NULL, 'L', NULL, 'held in 1 hand', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'When created, this mutagen is attuned to your choice of one of four energy types: acid, cold, electricity, or fire. When consumed, the mutagen suffuses your body with energy that spills out of you whenever you attack. At higher levels, it can even grant you the ability to unleash the energy in controlled bursts.<br><br><b>Benefit</b> You gain resistance to the attuned energy type. Whenever you score a hit with a melee weapon, add the listed amount of damage of the attuned energy type.<br><b>Drawback</b> You gain weakness 5 to the other three energy types.<br><br><b>Activate</b>  Interact<br><br><b>Energy Mutagen (Lesser) Item 1</b> <i>The Fall of Plaguestone pg. 56</i><br><b>Level</b> 1; <b>Price</b> 4 gp<br>You gain resistance 5, add 1 point of damage on a hit with a melee weapon, and the duration is 1 minute.<br><br><b>Energy Mutagen (Moderate) Item 3</b> <i>The Fall of Plaguestone pg. 56</i><br><b>Level</b> 3; <b>Price</b> 12 gp<br>You gain resistance 10, add 1d4 damage on a hit with a melee weapon, and the duration is 10 minutes.<br><br><b>Energy Mutagen (Greater) Item 11</b> <i>The Fall of Plaguestone pg. 56</i><br><b>Level</b> 11; <b>Price</b> 300 gp<br>You gain resistance 15, add 1d6 damage on a hit with a melee weapon, and the duration is 1 hour. In addition, you can end the benefits of this mutagen to unleash a 30-foot cone of energy that deals 2d6 damage of the attuned type for every full 10 minutes of duration remaining (DC 25 basic Reflex save).<br><br><b>Energy Mutagen (Major) Item 17</b> <i>The Fall of Plaguestone pg. 56</i><br><b>Level</b> 17; <b>Price</b> 3,000 gp<br>You gain resistance 20, add 2d6 damage on a hit with a melee weapon, and the duration is 1 hour. In addition, you can end the benefits of this mutagen to unleash a 30-foot cone of energy that deals 3d6 damage of the attuned type for every full 10 minutes of duration remaining (DC 32 basic Reflex save).', NULL, 'https://2e.aonprd.com/Equipment.aspx?ID=474'),
('ANTIPLAGUE_MODERATE', 'alchemical', 'Antiplague (Moderate)', '6', NULL, '35', NULL, 'L', NULL, 'held in 1 hand', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Antiplague can fortify the body’s defenses against diseases. Upon drinking an antiplague, you gain an item bonus to Fortitude saving throws against diseases for 24 hours; this applies to your daily save against a disease’s progression.<br><br><b>Activate</b>  Interact<br><br><b>Antiplague (Lesser) Item 1</b><br><b>Level</b> 1; <b>Price</b> 3 gp<br>You gain a +2 item bonus.<br><br><b>Antiplague (Moderate) Item 6</b><br><b>Level</b> 6; <b>Price</b> 35 gp<br>You gain a +3 item bonus.<br><br><b>Antiplague (Greater) Item 10</b><br><b>Level</b> 10; <b>Price</b> 160 gp<br>You gain a +4 item bonus.<br><br><b>Antiplague (Major) Item 14</b><br><b>Level</b> 14; <b>Price</b> 675 gp<br>You gain a +4 item bonus, and when you drink the antiplague, you can immediately attempt a saving throw against one disease of 14th level or lower affecting you. If you succeed, you are cured of the disease.', NULL, 'https://2e.aonprd.com/Equipment.aspx?ID=81'),
('SALAMANDER_ELIXIR_GREATER', 'alchemical', 'Salamander Elixir (Greater)', '16', NULL, '1400', NULL, 'L', NULL, 'held in 1 hand', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'This elixir is made from salamander scales to withstand fire. For 24 hours, you are protected from the effects of severe heat.<br><br><b>Activate</b>  Interact<br><br><b>Salamander Elixir (Lesser) Item 4</b><br><b>Level</b> 4; <b>Price</b> 15 gp<br><br><b>Salamander Elixir (Moderate) Item 12</b><br><b>Level</b> 12; <b>Price</b> 320 gp<br>You’re also protected from extreme heat.<br><br><b>Salamander Elixir (Greater) Item 16</b><br><b>Level</b> 16; <b>Price</b> 1,400 gp<br>You’re also protected from extreme and incredible heat.', NULL, 'https://2e.aonprd.com/Equipment.aspx?ID=98'),
