('QUICKSILVER_MUTAGEN_LESSER', 'alchemical', 'Quicksilver Mutagen (Lesser)', '1', NULL, '4', NULL, 'L', NULL, 'held in 1 hand', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Your features become thin and angular. You become swifter and nimbler, but your body also becomes&nbsp;fragile. <br><br><b>Benefit</b> You gain an item bonus to Acrobatics checks, Stealth checks, Thievery checks, Reflex saves, and ranged attack rolls, and you gain the listed status bonus to your Speed.<b>Drawback</b> You take damage equal to twice your level; you can’t recover Hit Points lost in this way by any means while the mutagen lasts. You take a –2 penalty to Fortitude saves.<br><br><b>Activate</b>  Interact<br><br><b>Quicksilver Mutagen (Lesser) Item 1</b><br><b>Level</b> 1; <b>Price</b> 4 gp<br>The bonus to rolls is +1, the bonus to Speed is +5 feet, and the duration is 1 minute.<br><br><b>Quicksilver Mutagen (Moderate) Item 3</b><br><b>Level</b> 3; <b>Price</b> 12 gp<br>The bonus to rolls is +2, the bonus to Speed is +10 feet, and the duration is 10 minutes.<br><br><b>Quicksilver Mutagen (Greater) Item 11</b><br><b>Level</b> 11; <b>Price</b> 300 gp<br>The bonus to rolls is +3, the bonus to Speed is +15 feet, and the duration is 1 hour.<br><br><b>Quicksilver Mutagen (Major) Item 17</b><br><b>Level</b> 17; <b>Price</b> 3,000 gp<br>The bonus to rolls is +4, the bonus to Speed is +20 feet, and the duration is 1 hour.', NULL, 'https://2e.aonprd.com/Equipment.aspx?ID=97'),
('SEA_TOUCH_ELIXIR_GREATER', 'alchemical', 'Sea Touch Elixir (Greater)', '15', NULL, '920', NULL, 'L', NULL, 'held in 1 hand', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'This briny concoction alters the skin on your hands and feet. The spaces between your fingers and toes become webbed, granting you a swim Speed of 20 feet for the listed duration.<br><br><b>Activate</b>  Interact<br><br><b>Sea Touch Elixir (Lesser) Item 5</b><br><b>Level</b> 5; <b>Price</b> 22 gp<br>The duration is 10 minutes.<br><br><b>Sea Touch Elixir (Moderate) Item 12</b><br><b>Level</b> 12; <b>Price</b> 300 gp<br>The duration is 1 hour, and you can breathe underwater.<br><br><b>Sea Touch Elixir (Greater) Item 15</b><br><b>Level</b> 15; <b>Price</b> 920 gp<br>The duration is 24 hours, and you can breathe underwater.', NULL, 'https://2e.aonprd.com/Equipment.aspx?ID=99'),
('ELIXIR_OF_LIFE_MODERATE', 'alchemical', 'Elixir of Life (Moderate)', '9', NULL, '150', NULL, 'L', NULL, 'held in 1 hand', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Elixirs of life accelerate the body’s natural healing processes and immune system. Upon drinking this elixir, you regain the listed number of Hit Points and gain an item bonus to saving throws against diseases and poisons for 10 minutes.<br><br><b>Activate</b>  Interact<br><br><b>Elixir of Life (Minor) Item 1</b><br><b>Level</b> 1; <b>Price</b> 3 gp<br>The elixir restores 1d6 Hit Points, and the bonus is +1.<br><br><b>Elixir of Life (Lesser) Item 5</b><br><b>Level</b> 5; <b>Price</b> 30 gp<br>The elixir restores 3d6+6 Hit Points and the bonus is +1.<br><br><b>Elixir of Life (Moderate) Item 9</b><br><b>Level</b> 9; <b>Price</b> 150 gp<br>The elixir restores 5d6+12 Hit Points, and the bonus is +2.<br><br><b>Elixir of Life (Greater) Item 13</b><br><b>Level</b> 13; <b>Price</b> 600 gp<br>The elixir restores 7d6+18 Hit Points, and the bonus is +2.<br><br><b>Elixir of Life (Major) Item 15</b><br><b>Level</b> 15; <b>Price</b> 1,300 gp<br>The elixir restores 8d6+21 Hit Points, and the bonus is +3.<br><br><b>Elixir of Life (True) Item 19</b><br><b>Level</b> 19; <b>Price</b> 3,000 gp<br>The elixir restores 10d6+27 Hit Points, and the bonus is +4.', NULL, 'https://2e.aonprd.com/Equipment.aspx?ID=91'),
('WINTER_WOLF_ELIXIR_GREATER', 'alchemical', 'Winter Wolf Elixir (Greater)', '16', NULL, '1400', NULL, 'L', NULL, 'held in 1 hand', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'This elixir warms your core and improves your circulation. For 24 hours, you are protected from the effects of severe cold.<br><br><b>Activate</b>  Interact<br><br><b>Winter Wolf Elixir (Lesser) Item 4</b><br><b>Level</b> 4; <b>Price</b> 15 gp<br><br><b>Winter Wolf Elixir (Moderate) Item 12</b><br><b>Level</b> 12; <b>Price</b> 320 gp<br>You’re also protected from extreme cold.<br><br><b>Winter Wolf Elixir (Greater) Item 16</b><br><b>Level</b> 16; <b>Price</b> 1,400 gp<br>You’re also protected from extreme and incredible cold.', NULL, 'https://2e.aonprd.com/Equipment.aspx?ID=103'),
('ANTIDOTE_LESSER', 'alchemical', 'Antidote (Lesser)', '1', NULL, '3', NULL, 'L', NULL, 'held in 1 hand', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'An antidote protects you against toxins. Upon drinking an antidote, you gain an item bonus to Fortitude saving throws against poisons for 6 hours.<br><br><b>Activate</b>  Interact<br><br><b>Antidote (Lesser) Item 1</b><br><b>Level</b> 1; <b>Price</b> 3 gp<br>You gain a +2 item bonus.<br><br><b>Antidote (Moderate) Item 6</b><br><b>Level</b> 6; <b>Price</b> 35 gp<br>You gain a +3 item bonus.<br><br><b>Antidote (Greater) Item 10</b><br><b>Level</b> 10; <b>Price</b> 160 gp<br>You gain a +4 item bonus.<br><br><b>Antidote (Major) Item 14</b><br><b>Level</b> 14; <b>Price</b> 675 gp<br>You gain a +4 item bonus, and when you drink the antidote, you can immediately attempt a saving throw against one poison of 14th level or lower affecting you. If you succeed, the poison is neutralized.', NULL, 'https://2e.aonprd.com/Equipment.aspx?ID=80'),
('BESTIAL_MUTAGEN_MAJOR', 'alchemical', 'Bestial Mutagen (Major)', '17', NULL, '3000', NULL, 'L', NULL, 'held in 1 hand', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Your features transform into something bestial and you take on muscle mass, but your lumbering form is clumsy. <br><br><b>Benefit</b> You gain an item bonus to Athletics checks and unarmed attack rolls. You gain a claw unarmed attack with the agile trait and a jaws unarmed attack. <br><br><b>Drawback</b> You take a –1 penalty to AC and a –2 penalty to Reflex saves.<br><br><b>Activate</b>  Interact<br><br><b>Bestial Mutagen (Lesser) Item 1</b><br><b>Level</b> 1; <b>Price</b> 4 gp<br>You gain a +1 item bonus, your claw deals 1d4 slashing damage, your jaws deal 1d6 piercing damage, and the duration is 1 minute.<br><br><b>Bestial Mutagen (Moderate) Item 3</b><br><b>Level</b> 3; <b>Price</b> 12 gp<br>You gain a +2 item bonus, your claw deals 1d6 slashing damage, your jaws deal 1d8 piercing damage, and the duration is 10 minutes.<br><br><b>Bestial Mutagen (Greater) Item 11</b><br><b>Level</b> 11; <b>Price</b> 300 gp<br>You gain a +3 item bonus, your claw deals 1d8 slashing damage, your jaws deal 1d10 piercing damage, and the duration is 1 hour.<br><br><b>Bestial Mutagen (Major) Item 17</b><br><b>Level</b> 17; <b>Price</b> 3,000 gp<br>You gain a +4 item bonus, your claw deals 1d8 slashing damage, your jaws deal 1d10 piercing damage, and the duration is 1 hour. You gain weapon specialization with the claws and jaws, or greater weapon specialization, if you already have weapon specialization with these unarmed attacks.', NULL, 'https://2e.aonprd.com/Equipment.aspx?ID=82'),
('DARKVISION_ELIXIR_GREATER', 'alchemical', 'Darkvision Elixir (Greater)', '8', NULL, '90', NULL, 'L', NULL, 'held in 1 hand', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'After you drink this elixir, your sight becomes sharper in darkness. You gain darkvision for the listed duration.<br><br><b>Activate</b>  Interact<br><br><b>Darkvision Elixir (Lesser) Item 2</b><br><b>Level</b> 2; <b>Price</b> 6 gp<br>The duration is 10 minutes.<br><br><b>Darkvision Elixir (Moderate) Item 4</b><br><b>Level</b> 4; <b>Price</b> 11 gp<br>The duration is 1 hour.<br><br><b>Darkvision Elixir (Greater) Item 8</b><br><b>Level</b> 8; <b>Price</b> 90 gp<br>The duration is 24 hours.', NULL, 'https://2e.aonprd.com/Equipment.aspx?ID=89'),
('SERENE_MUTAGEN_MAJOR', 'alchemical', 'Serene Mutagen (Major)', '17', NULL, '3000', NULL, 'L', NULL, 'held in 1 hand', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'You gain inner serenity, focused on fine details and steeled against mental assaults, but you find violence off-putting.<br><br><b>Benefit</b> You gain an item bonus to Will saves and Perception, Medicine, Nature, Religion, and Survival checks. This bonus improves when you attempt Will saves against mental effects. <br><br><b>Drawback</b> You take a –1 penalty to attack rolls and save DCs of offensive spells, and a –1 penalty per damage die to all weapon, unarmed attack, and spell damage.<br><br><b>Activate</b>  Interact<br><br><b>Serene Mutagen (Lesser) Item 1</b><br><b>Level</b> 1; <b>Price</b> 4 gp<br>The bonus is +1, or +2 vs. mental, and the duration is 1 minute.<br><br><b>Serene Mutagen (Moderate) Item 3</b><br><b>Level</b> 3; <b>Price</b> 12 gp<br>The bonus is +2, or +3 vs. mental, and the duration is 10 minutes.<br><br><b>Serene Mutagen (Greater) Item 11</b><br><b>Level</b> 11; <b>Price</b> 300 gp<br>The bonus is +2, or +3 vs. mental, and the duration is 10 minutes.<br><br><b>Serene Mutagen (Major) Item 17</b><br><b>Level</b> 17; <b>Price</b> 3,000 gp<br>The bonus is +4, and the duration is 1 hour. When you roll a success on a Will save against a mental effect, you get a critical success instead, and your critical failures on Will saves against mental effects become failures instead.', NULL, 'https://2e.aonprd.com/Equipment.aspx?ID=100'),
('CHEETAH_S_ELIXIR_MODERATE', 'alchemical', 'Cheetah''s Elixir (Moderate)', '5', NULL, '25', NULL, 'L', NULL, 'held in 1 hand', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Enzymatic compounds in this elixir strengthen and excite the muscles in your legs. You gain a status bonus to your Speed for the listed duration.<br><br><b>Activate</b>  Interact<br><br><b>Cheetah''s Elixir (Lesser) Item 1</b><br><b>Level</b> 1; <b>Price</b> 3 gp<br>The bonus is +5 feet, and the duration is 1 minute.<br><br><b>Cheetah''s Elixir (Moderate) Item 5</b><br><b>Level</b> 5; <b>Price</b> 25 gp<br>The bonus is +10 feet, and the duration is 10 minutes.<br><br><b>Cheetah''s Elixir (Greater) Item 9</b><br><b>Level</b> 9; <b>Price</b> 110 gp<br>The bonus is +10 feet, and the duration is 1 hour.', NULL, 'https://2e.aonprd.com/Equipment.aspx?ID=86'),
('LEAPER_S_ELIXIR_GREATER', 'alchemical', 'Leaper''s Elixir (Greater)', '7', NULL, '55', NULL, 'L', NULL, 'held in 1 hand', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'This tingly solution increases the elasticity and contraction of your leg muscles. For 1 minute after drinking this elixir, you can High Jump or Long Jump as a single action instead of 2 actions. If you do, you don’t perform the initial Stride (nor do you fail if you don’t Stride 10 feet).<br><br><b>Activate</b>  Interact<br><br><b>Leaper''s Elixir (Lesser) Item 1</b><br><b>Level</b> 1; <b>Price</b> 3 gp<br><br><b>Leaper''s Elixir (Greater) Item 7</b><br><b>Level</b> 7; <b>Price</b> 55 gp<br>The maximum vertical distance you can jump with a High Jump is the same as you can jump horizontally with a Long Jump.', NULL, 'https://2e.aonprd.com/Equipment.aspx?ID=95'),
('ELIXIR_OF_LIFE_TRUE', 'alchemical', 'Elixir of Life (True)', '19', NULL, '3000', NULL, 'L', NULL, 'held in 1 hand', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Elixirs of life accelerate the body’s natural healing processes and immune system. Upon drinking this elixir, you regain the listed number of Hit Points and gain an item bonus to saving throws against diseases and poisons for 10 minutes.<br><br><b>Activate</b>  Interact<br><br><b>Elixir of Life (Minor) Item 1</b><br><b>Level</b> 1; <b>Price</b> 3 gp<br>The elixir restores 1d6 Hit Points, and the bonus is +1.<br><br><b>Elixir of Life (Lesser) Item 5</b><br><b>Level</b> 5; <b>Price</b> 30 gp<br>The elixir restores 3d6+6 Hit Points and the bonus is +1.<br><br><b>Elixir of Life (Moderate) Item 9</b><br><b>Level</b> 9; <b>Price</b> 150 gp<br>The elixir restores 5d6+12 Hit Points, and the bonus is +2.<br><br><b>Elixir of Life (Greater) Item 13</b><br><b>Level</b> 13; <b>Price</b> 600 gp<br>The elixir restores 7d6+18 Hit Points, and the bonus is +2.<br><br><b>Elixir of Life (Major) Item 15</b><br><b>Level</b> 15; <b>Price</b> 1,300 gp<br>The elixir restores 8d6+21 Hit Points, and the bonus is +3.<br><br><b>Elixir of Life (True) Item 19</b><br><b>Level</b> 19; <b>Price</b> 3,000 gp<br>The elixir restores 10d6+27 Hit Points, and the bonus is +4.', NULL, 'https://2e.aonprd.com/Equipment.aspx?ID=91'),
('SILVERTONGUE_MUTAGEN_MODERATE', 'alchemical', 'Silvertongue Mutagen (Moderate)', '3', NULL, '12', NULL, 'L', NULL, 'held in 1 hand', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Your features become striking and your voice becomes musical and commanding, though facts and figures become hazy for you and emotion clouds your ability to reason.<b>Benefit</b> You gain an item bonus to Deception, Diplomacy, Intimidation, and Performance checks. Your critical failures with any of these skill become failures instead.<b>Drawback</b> You take a –2 item penalty to Arcana, Crafting, Lore, Occultism, and Society checks. Choose one skill in which you are trained; for the duration, you become untrained in that skill. All your failures on checks to Recall Knowledge become critical failures.<br><br><b>Activate</b>  Interact<br><br><b>Silvertongue Mutagen (Lesser) Item 1</b><br><b>Level</b> 1; <b>Price</b> 4 gp<br>The bonus is +1, and the duration is 1 minute.<br><br><b>Silvertongue Mutagen (Moderate) Item 3</b><br><b>Level</b> 3; <b>Price</b> 12 gp<br>The bonus is +2, and the duration is 10 minutes.<br><br><b>Silvertongue Mutagen (Greater) Item 11</b><br><b>Level</b> 11; <b>Price</b> 300 gp<br>The bonus is +3, and the duration is 1 hour.<br><br><b>Silvertongue Mutagen (Major) Item 17</b><br><b>Level</b> 17; <b>Price</b> 3,000 gp<br>The bonus is +4, and the duration is 1 hour.', NULL, 'https://2e.aonprd.com/Equipment.aspx?ID=101'),
