('JUGGERNAUT_MUTAGEN_MAJOR', 'alchemical', 'Juggernaut Mutagen (Major)', '17', NULL, '3000', NULL, 'L', NULL, 'held in 1 hand', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'After you drink this mutagen, your body becomes thick and sturdy. You exhibit a healthy glow, though you tend to be ponderous and unobservant. <br><br><b>Benefit</b> You gain an item bonus to Fortitude saves and the listed number of temporary Hit Points. Whenever you are at maximum Hit Points for at least 1 full minute, you regain the temporary Hit Points. <br><br><b>Drawback</b> You take a –2 penalty to Will saves, Perception checks, and initiative rolls. <br><br><b>Activate</b>  Interact<br><br><b>Juggernaut Mutagen (Lesser) Item 1</b><br><b>Level</b> 1; <b>Price</b> 4 gp<br>The bonus is +1, you gain 5 temporary Hit Points, and the duration is 1 minute.<br><br><b>Juggernaut Mutagen (Moderate) Item 3</b><br><b>Level</b> 3; <b>Price</b> 12 gp<br>The bonus is +2, you gain 10 temporary Hit Points, and the duration is 10 minutes.<br><br><b>Juggernaut Mutagen (Greater) Item 11</b><br><b>Level</b> 11; <b>Price</b> 300 gp<br>The bonus is +3, you gain 30 temporary Hit Points, and the duration is 1 hour. When you roll a success on a Fortitude save, you get a critical success instead.<br><br><b>Juggernaut Mutagen (Major) Item 17</b><br><b>Level</b> 17; <b>Price</b> 3,000 gp<br>The bonus is +4, you gain 45 temporary Hit Points, and the duration is 1 hour. When you roll a success on a Fortitude save, you get a critical success instead, and your critical failures on Fortitude saves become failures instead.', NULL, 'https://2e.aonprd.com/Equipment.aspx?ID=94'),
('EAGLE_EYE_ELIXIR_MAJOR', 'alchemical', 'Eagle Eye Elixir (Major)', '16', NULL, '2000', NULL, 'L', NULL, 'held in 1 hand', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'After you drink this elixir, you notice subtle visual details. For the next hour, you gain an item bonus to Perception checks that is greater when attempting to find secret doors and traps. <br><br><b>Activate</b>  Interact<br><br><b>Eagle Eye Elixir (Lesser) Item 1</b><br><b>Level</b> 1; <b>Price</b> 4 gp<br>The bonus is +1, or +2 to find secret doors and traps.<br><br><b>Eagle Eye Elixir (Moderate) Item 5</b><br><b>Level</b> 5; <b>Price</b> 27 gp<br>The bonus is +2, or +3 to find secret doors and traps.<br><br><b>Eagle Eye Elixir (Greater) Item 10</b><br><b>Level</b> 10; <b>Price</b> 200 gp<br>The bonus is +3, or +4 to find secret doors and traps.<br><br><b>Eagle Eye Elixir (Major) Item 16</b><br><b>Level</b> 16; <b>Price</b> 2,000 gp<br>The bonus is +3, or +4 to find secret doors and traps. Each time you pass within 10 feet of a secret door or trap, the GM automatically rolls a secret check for you to find it.', NULL, 'https://2e.aonprd.com/Equipment.aspx?ID=90'),
('JUGGERNAUT_MUTAGEN_LESSER', 'alchemical', 'Juggernaut Mutagen (Lesser)', '1', NULL, '4', NULL, 'L', NULL, 'held in 1 hand', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'After you drink this mutagen, your body becomes thick and sturdy. You exhibit a healthy glow, though you tend to be ponderous and unobservant. <br><br><b>Benefit</b> You gain an item bonus to Fortitude saves and the listed number of temporary Hit Points. Whenever you are at maximum Hit Points for at least 1 full minute, you regain the temporary Hit Points. <br><br><b>Drawback</b> You take a –2 penalty to Will saves, Perception checks, and initiative rolls. <br><br><b>Activate</b>  Interact<br><br><b>Juggernaut Mutagen (Lesser) Item 1</b><br><b>Level</b> 1; <b>Price</b> 4 gp<br>The bonus is +1, you gain 5 temporary Hit Points, and the duration is 1 minute.<br><br><b>Juggernaut Mutagen (Moderate) Item 3</b><br><b>Level</b> 3; <b>Price</b> 12 gp<br>The bonus is +2, you gain 10 temporary Hit Points, and the duration is 10 minutes.<br><br><b>Juggernaut Mutagen (Greater) Item 11</b><br><b>Level</b> 11; <b>Price</b> 300 gp<br>The bonus is +3, you gain 30 temporary Hit Points, and the duration is 1 hour. When you roll a success on a Fortitude save, you get a critical success instead.<br><br><b>Juggernaut Mutagen (Major) Item 17</b><br><b>Level</b> 17; <b>Price</b> 3,000 gp<br>The bonus is +4, you gain 45 temporary Hit Points, and the duration is 1 hour. When you roll a success on a Fortitude save, you get a critical success instead, and your critical failures on Fortitude saves become failures instead.', NULL, 'https://2e.aonprd.com/Equipment.aspx?ID=94'),
('ENERGY_MUTAGEN_MODERATE', 'alchemical', 'Energy Mutagen (Moderate)', '3', NULL, '12', NULL, 'L', NULL, 'held in 1 hand', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'When created, this mutagen is attuned to your choice of one of four energy types: acid, cold, electricity, or fire. When consumed, the mutagen suffuses your body with energy that spills out of you whenever you attack. At higher levels, it can even grant you the ability to unleash the energy in controlled bursts.<br><br><b>Benefit</b> You gain resistance to the attuned energy type. Whenever you score a hit with a melee weapon, add the listed amount of damage of the attuned energy type.<br><b>Drawback</b> You gain weakness 5 to the other three energy types.<br><br><b>Activate</b>  Interact<br><br><b>Energy Mutagen (Lesser) Item 1</b> <i>The Fall of Plaguestone pg. 56</i><br><b>Level</b> 1; <b>Price</b> 4 gp<br>You gain resistance 5, add 1 point of damage on a hit with a melee weapon, and the duration is 1 minute.<br><br><b>Energy Mutagen (Moderate) Item 3</b> <i>The Fall of Plaguestone pg. 56</i><br><b>Level</b> 3; <b>Price</b> 12 gp<br>You gain resistance 10, add 1d4 damage on a hit with a melee weapon, and the duration is 10 minutes.<br><br><b>Energy Mutagen (Greater) Item 11</b> <i>The Fall of Plaguestone pg. 56</i><br><b>Level</b> 11; <b>Price</b> 300 gp<br>You gain resistance 15, add 1d6 damage on a hit with a melee weapon, and the duration is 1 hour. In addition, you can end the benefits of this mutagen to unleash a 30-foot cone of energy that deals 2d6 damage of the attuned type for every full 10 minutes of duration remaining (DC 25 basic Reflex save).<br><br><b>Energy Mutagen (Major) Item 17</b> <i>The Fall of Plaguestone pg. 56</i><br><b>Level</b> 17; <b>Price</b> 3,000 gp<br>You gain resistance 20, add 2d6 damage on a hit with a melee weapon, and the duration is 1 hour. In addition, you can end the benefits of this mutagen to unleash a 30-foot cone of energy that deals 3d6 damage of the attuned type for every full 10 minutes of duration remaining (DC 32 basic Reflex save).', NULL, 'https://2e.aonprd.com/Equipment.aspx?ID=474'),
('MISTFORM_ELIXIR_MODERATE', 'alchemical', 'Mistform Elixir (Moderate)', '6', NULL, '56', NULL, 'L', NULL, 'held in 1 hand', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'A faint mist emanates from your skin, making you concealed for the listed duration. As usual being concealed when your position is still obvious, you can’t use this concealment to Hide or Sneak.<br><br><b>Activate</b>  Interact<br><br><b>Mistform Elixir (Lesser) Item 4</b><br><b>Level</b> 4; <b>Price</b> 18 gp<br>The duration is 3 rounds.<br><br><b>Mistform Elixir (Moderate) Item 6</b><br><b>Level</b> 6; <b>Price</b> 56 gp<br>The duration is 1 minute.<br><br><b>Mistform Elixir (Greater) Item 10</b><br><b>Level</b> 10; <b>Price</b> 180 gp<br>The duration is 5 minutes.', NULL, 'https://2e.aonprd.com/Equipment.aspx?ID=96'),
('JUGGERNAUT_MUTAGEN_GREATER', 'alchemical', 'Juggernaut Mutagen (Greater)', '11', NULL, '300', NULL, 'L', NULL, 'held in 1 hand', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'After you drink this mutagen, your body becomes thick and sturdy. You exhibit a healthy glow, though you tend to be ponderous and unobservant. <br><br><b>Benefit</b> You gain an item bonus to Fortitude saves and the listed number of temporary Hit Points. Whenever you are at maximum Hit Points for at least 1 full minute, you regain the temporary Hit Points. <br><br><b>Drawback</b> You take a –2 penalty to Will saves, Perception checks, and initiative rolls. <br><br><b>Activate</b>  Interact<br><br><b>Juggernaut Mutagen (Lesser) Item 1</b><br><b>Level</b> 1; <b>Price</b> 4 gp<br>The bonus is +1, you gain 5 temporary Hit Points, and the duration is 1 minute.<br><br><b>Juggernaut Mutagen (Moderate) Item 3</b><br><b>Level</b> 3; <b>Price</b> 12 gp<br>The bonus is +2, you gain 10 temporary Hit Points, and the duration is 10 minutes.<br><br><b>Juggernaut Mutagen (Greater) Item 11</b><br><b>Level</b> 11; <b>Price</b> 300 gp<br>The bonus is +3, you gain 30 temporary Hit Points, and the duration is 1 hour. When you roll a success on a Fortitude save, you get a critical success instead.<br><br><b>Juggernaut Mutagen (Major) Item 17</b><br><b>Level</b> 17; <b>Price</b> 3,000 gp<br>The bonus is +4, you gain 45 temporary Hit Points, and the duration is 1 hour. When you roll a success on a Fortitude save, you get a critical success instead, and your critical failures on Fortitude saves become failures instead.', NULL, 'https://2e.aonprd.com/Equipment.aspx?ID=94'),
('EAGLE_EYE_ELIXIR_GREATER', 'alchemical', 'Eagle Eye Elixir (Greater)', '10', NULL, '200', NULL, 'L', NULL, 'held in 1 hand', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'After you drink this elixir, you notice subtle visual details. For the next hour, you gain an item bonus to Perception checks that is greater when attempting to find secret doors and traps. <br><br><b>Activate</b>  Interact<br><br><b>Eagle Eye Elixir (Lesser) Item 1</b><br><b>Level</b> 1; <b>Price</b> 4 gp<br>The bonus is +1, or +2 to find secret doors and traps.<br><br><b>Eagle Eye Elixir (Moderate) Item 5</b><br><b>Level</b> 5; <b>Price</b> 27 gp<br>The bonus is +2, or +3 to find secret doors and traps.<br><br><b>Eagle Eye Elixir (Greater) Item 10</b><br><b>Level</b> 10; <b>Price</b> 200 gp<br>The bonus is +3, or +4 to find secret doors and traps.<br><br><b>Eagle Eye Elixir (Major) Item 16</b><br><b>Level</b> 16; <b>Price</b> 2,000 gp<br>The bonus is +3, or +4 to find secret doors and traps. Each time you pass within 10 feet of a secret door or trap, the GM automatically rolls a secret check for you to find it.', NULL, 'https://2e.aonprd.com/Equipment.aspx?ID=90'),
('SILVERTONGUE_MUTAGEN_GREATER', 'alchemical', 'Silvertongue Mutagen (Greater)', '11', NULL, '300', NULL, 'L', NULL, 'held in 1 hand', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Your features become striking and your voice becomes musical and commanding, though facts and figures become hazy for you and emotion clouds your ability to reason.<b>Benefit</b> You gain an item bonus to Deception, Diplomacy, Intimidation, and Performance checks. Your critical failures with any of these skill become failures instead.<b>Drawback</b> You take a –2 item penalty to Arcana, Crafting, Lore, Occultism, and Society checks. Choose one skill in which you are trained; for the duration, you become untrained in that skill. All your failures on checks to Recall Knowledge become critical failures.<br><br><b>Activate</b>  Interact<br><br><b>Silvertongue Mutagen (Lesser) Item 1</b><br><b>Level</b> 1; <b>Price</b> 4 gp<br>The bonus is +1, and the duration is 1 minute.<br><br><b>Silvertongue Mutagen (Moderate) Item 3</b><br><b>Level</b> 3; <b>Price</b> 12 gp<br>The bonus is +2, and the duration is 10 minutes.<br><br><b>Silvertongue Mutagen (Greater) Item 11</b><br><b>Level</b> 11; <b>Price</b> 300 gp<br>The bonus is +3, and the duration is 1 hour.<br><br><b>Silvertongue Mutagen (Major) Item 17</b><br><b>Level</b> 17; <b>Price</b> 3,000 gp<br>The bonus is +4, and the duration is 1 hour.', NULL, 'https://2e.aonprd.com/Equipment.aspx?ID=101'),
('BRAVO_S_BREW_MODERATE', 'alchemical', 'Bravo''s Brew (Moderate)', '10', NULL, '150', NULL, 'L', NULL, 'held in 1 hand', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'This flask of foaming beer grants courage. For the next hour after drinking this elixir, you gain an item bonus to Will saves, which is greater when attempting Will saves against fear.<br><br><b>Activate</b>  Interact<br><br><b>Bravo''s Brew (Lesser) Item 2</b><br><b>Level</b> 2; <b>Price</b> 7 gp<br>The bonus on Will saves is +1, or +2 against fear.<br><br><b>Bravo''s Brew (Moderate) Item 10</b><br><b>Level</b> 10; <b>Price</b> 150 gp<br>The bonus on Will saves is +2, or +3 against fear.<br><br><b>Bravo''s Brew (Greater) Item 15</b><br><b>Level</b> 15; <b>Price</b> 700 gp<br>The bonus on Will saves is +3, or +4 against fear. If you roll a success on a save against fear, you get a critical success&nbsp;instead.', NULL, 'https://2e.aonprd.com/Equipment.aspx?ID=84'),
('ENERGY_MUTAGEN_GREATER', 'alchemical', 'Energy Mutagen (Greater)', '11', NULL, '300', NULL, 'L', NULL, 'held in 1 hand', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'When created, this mutagen is attuned to your choice of one of four energy types: acid, cold, electricity, or fire. When consumed, the mutagen suffuses your body with energy that spills out of you whenever you attack. At higher levels, it can even grant you the ability to unleash the energy in controlled bursts.<br><br><b>Benefit</b> You gain resistance to the attuned energy type. Whenever you score a hit with a melee weapon, add the listed amount of damage of the attuned energy type.<br><b>Drawback</b> You gain weakness 5 to the other three energy types.<br><br><b>Activate</b>  Interact<br><br><b>Energy Mutagen (Lesser) Item 1</b> <i>The Fall of Plaguestone pg. 56</i><br><b>Level</b> 1; <b>Price</b> 4 gp<br>You gain resistance 5, add 1 point of damage on a hit with a melee weapon, and the duration is 1 minute.<br><br><b>Energy Mutagen (Moderate) Item 3</b> <i>The Fall of Plaguestone pg. 56</i><br><b>Level</b> 3; <b>Price</b> 12 gp<br>You gain resistance 10, add 1d4 damage on a hit with a melee weapon, and the duration is 10 minutes.<br><br><b>Energy Mutagen (Greater) Item 11</b> <i>The Fall of Plaguestone pg. 56</i><br><b>Level</b> 11; <b>Price</b> 300 gp<br>You gain resistance 15, add 1d6 damage on a hit with a melee weapon, and the duration is 1 hour. In addition, you can end the benefits of this mutagen to unleash a 30-foot cone of energy that deals 2d6 damage of the attuned type for every full 10 minutes of duration remaining (DC 25 basic Reflex save).<br><br><b>Energy Mutagen (Major) Item 17</b> <i>The Fall of Plaguestone pg. 56</i><br><b>Level</b> 17; <b>Price</b> 3,000 gp<br>You gain resistance 20, add 2d6 damage on a hit with a melee weapon, and the duration is 1 hour. In addition, you can end the benefits of this mutagen to unleash a 30-foot cone of energy that deals 3d6 damage of the attuned type for every full 10 minutes of duration remaining (DC 32 basic Reflex save).', NULL, 'https://2e.aonprd.com/Equipment.aspx?ID=474'),
('ANTIDOTE_GREATER', 'alchemical', 'Antidote (Greater)', '10', NULL, '160', NULL, 'L', NULL, 'held in 1 hand', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'An antidote protects you against toxins. Upon drinking an antidote, you gain an item bonus to Fortitude saving throws against poisons for 6 hours.<br><br><b>Activate</b>  Interact<br><br><b>Antidote (Lesser) Item 1</b><br><b>Level</b> 1; <b>Price</b> 3 gp<br>You gain a +2 item bonus.<br><br><b>Antidote (Moderate) Item 6</b><br><b>Level</b> 6; <b>Price</b> 35 gp<br>You gain a +3 item bonus.<br><br><b>Antidote (Greater) Item 10</b><br><b>Level</b> 10; <b>Price</b> 160 gp<br>You gain a +4 item bonus.<br><br><b>Antidote (Major) Item 14</b><br><b>Level</b> 14; <b>Price</b> 675 gp<br>You gain a +4 item bonus, and when you drink the antidote, you can immediately attempt a saving throw against one poison of 14th level or lower affecting you. If you succeed, the poison is neutralized.', NULL, 'https://2e.aonprd.com/Equipment.aspx?ID=80'),
('SALAMANDER_ELIXIR_LESSER', 'alchemical', 'Salamander Elixir (Lesser)', '4', NULL, '15', NULL, 'L', NULL, 'held in 1 hand', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'This elixir is made from salamander scales to withstand fire. For 24 hours, you are protected from the effects of severe heat.<br><br><b>Activate</b>  Interact<br><br><b>Salamander Elixir (Lesser) Item 4</b><br><b>Level</b> 4; <b>Price</b> 15 gp<br><br><b>Salamander Elixir (Moderate) Item 12</b><br><b>Level</b> 12; <b>Price</b> 320 gp<br>You’re also protected from extreme heat.<br><br><b>Salamander Elixir (Greater) Item 16</b><br><b>Level</b> 16; <b>Price</b> 1,400 gp<br>You’re also protected from extreme and incredible heat.', NULL, 'https://2e.aonprd.com/Equipment.aspx?ID=98'),
('ANTIPLAGUE_LESSER', 'alchemical', 'Antiplague (Lesser)', '1', NULL, '3', NULL, 'L', NULL, 'held in 1 hand', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Antiplague can fortify the body’s defenses against diseases. Upon drinking an antiplague, you gain an item bonus to Fortitude saving throws against diseases for 24 hours; this applies to your daily save against a disease’s progression.<br><br><b>Activate</b>  Interact<br><br><b>Antiplague (Lesser) Item 1</b><br><b>Level</b> 1; <b>Price</b> 3 gp<br>You gain a +2 item bonus.<br><br><b>Antiplague (Moderate) Item 6</b><br><b>Level</b> 6; <b>Price</b> 35 gp<br>You gain a +3 item bonus.<br><br><b>Antiplague (Greater) Item 10</b><br><b>Level</b> 10; <b>Price</b> 160 gp<br>You gain a +4 item bonus.<br><br><b>Antiplague (Major) Item 14</b><br><b>Level</b> 14; <b>Price</b> 675 gp<br>You gain a +4 item bonus, and when you drink the antiplague, you can immediately attempt a saving throw against one disease of 14th level or lower affecting you. If you succeed, you are cured of the disease.', NULL, 'https://2e.aonprd.com/Equipment.aspx?ID=81'),
('ELIXIR_OF_REJUVENATION', 'alchemical', 'Elixir of Rejuvenation', '20', NULL, '0', NULL, 'L', NULL, 'held in 1 hand', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'The elixir of rejuvenation restores a creature to full health and eradicates toxins affecting it. When you drink this elixir, you’re restored to your maximum Hit Points, and all afflictions of 20th level or lower affecting you are removed.<br><br> You can instead administer this elixir to a creature that has been dead for a week or less. When you do, that creature is instantly brought back to life with 1 Hit Point and no spell slots, Focus Points, or other daily resources.<br><br><b>Activate</b>  Interact<br><br><b>Craft Requirements</b> philosopher’s stone, true elixir of life', NULL, 'https://2e.aonprd.com/Equipment.aspx?ID=92'),
('BESTIAL_MUTAGEN_LESSER', 'alchemical', 'Bestial Mutagen (Lesser)', '1', NULL, '4', NULL, 'L', NULL, 'held in 1 hand', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Your features transform into something bestial and you take on muscle mass, but your lumbering form is clumsy. <br><br><b>Benefit</b> You gain an item bonus to Athletics checks and unarmed attack rolls. You gain a claw unarmed attack with the agile trait and a jaws unarmed attack. <br><br><b>Drawback</b> You take a –1 penalty to AC and a –2 penalty to Reflex saves.<br><br><b>Activate</b>  Interact<br><br><b>Bestial Mutagen (Lesser) Item 1</b><br><b>Level</b> 1; <b>Price</b> 4 gp<br>You gain a +1 item bonus, your claw deals 1d4 slashing damage, your jaws deal 1d6 piercing damage, and the duration is 1 minute.<br><br><b>Bestial Mutagen (Moderate) Item 3</b><br><b>Level</b> 3; <b>Price</b> 12 gp<br>You gain a +2 item bonus, your claw deals 1d6 slashing damage, your jaws deal 1d8 piercing damage, and the duration is 10 minutes.<br><br><b>Bestial Mutagen (Greater) Item 11</b><br><b>Level</b> 11; <b>Price</b> 300 gp<br>You gain a +3 item bonus, your claw deals 1d8 slashing damage, your jaws deal 1d10 piercing damage, and the duration is 1 hour.<br><br><b>Bestial Mutagen (Major) Item 17</b><br><b>Level</b> 17; <b>Price</b> 3,000 gp<br>You gain a +4 item bonus, your claw deals 1d8 slashing damage, your jaws deal 1d10 piercing damage, and the duration is 1 hour. You gain weapon specialization with the claws and jaws, or greater weapon specialization, if you already have weapon specialization with these unarmed attacks.', NULL, 'https://2e.aonprd.com/Equipment.aspx?ID=82'),
('SEA_TOUCH_ELIXIR_LESSER', 'alchemical', 'Sea Touch Elixir (Lesser)', '5', NULL, '22', NULL, 'L', NULL, 'held in 1 hand', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'This briny concoction alters the skin on your hands and feet. The spaces between your fingers and toes become webbed, granting you a swim Speed of 20 feet for the listed duration.<br><br><b>Activate</b>  Interact<br><br><b>Sea Touch Elixir (Lesser) Item 5</b><br><b>Level</b> 5; <b>Price</b> 22 gp<br>The duration is 10 minutes.<br><br><b>Sea Touch Elixir (Moderate) Item 12</b><br><b>Level</b> 12; <b>Price</b> 300 gp<br>The duration is 1 hour, and you can breathe underwater.<br><br><b>Sea Touch Elixir (Greater) Item 15</b><br><b>Level</b> 15; <b>Price</b> 920 gp<br>The duration is 24 hours, and you can breathe underwater.', NULL, 'https://2e.aonprd.com/Equipment.aspx?ID=99'),
